{
  "id": "5bc4910555b315001372f0a9",
  "title": "CNNと自己注意",
  "created": 1539608840,
  "updated": 1539680259,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5bc4910555b315001372f0a9",
      "text": "CNNと自己注意",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539608840,
      "updated": 1539608840
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49108aff09e00006ae3c5",
      "text": " 固定長の入力しか受け取れなかった[CNN]が不定長の入力を受け取れる[注意機構]で置き換えられた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539608840,
      "updated": 1539608854
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49110aff09e00006ae3c6",
      "text": " なぜ不定長への拡張ができるのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539608848,
      "updated": 1539608949
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc4911baff09e00006ae3c8",
      "text": " CNNは、自分からの相対位置で、どの位置の値にどんな重みを掛けるかは行列の形でハードコードされていた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539608860,
      "updated": 1539609020
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49222aff09e00006ae3cb",
      "text": " \tなので前後何個の値に対して処理をするかを事前に固定する必要があった[https://gyazo.com/adfdef7c11d9c8c05bb40d3be79eefbd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609123,
      "updated": 1539679689
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5a5c9aff09e0000f76aa0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539679689,
      "updated": 1539679689
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc491bcaff09e00006ae3c9",
      "text": " 注意機構では、どんな重みを掛けるかは、その値によって決まる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609020,
      "updated": 1539609063
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc491c1aff09e00006ae3ca",
      "text": "\t だから個数を事前に定める必要がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609026,
      "updated": 1539609157
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5a803aff09e0000f76aa1",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/1902ffd4c16d50ff825b1b2573fdc97e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539680258,
      "updated": 1539680259
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5a804aff09e0000f76aa2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539680259,
      "updated": 1539680259
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49245aff09e00006ae3cc",
      "text": "  その代わり、単純な構成では位置の情報がないので入力列をシャッフルしても注意機構が返す値は同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609157,
      "updated": 1539609183
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57098aff09e0000b3a2c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666072,
      "updated": 1539666072
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49262aff09e00006ae3ce",
      "text": "\t[Transformer]では[Positional Encoding]を組み合わせる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609186,
      "updated": 1539666079
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc492a4aff09e00006ae3cf",
      "text": " \t入力値自体に位置の情報を埋め込んでしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609253,
      "updated": 1539609257
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc492a8aff09e00006ae3d0",
      "text": "  これで注意機構がCNNの代わりを果たせるようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539609257,
      "updated": 1539609259
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc49119aff09e00006ae3c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539608857,
      "updated": 1539608857
    }
  ]
}